{"tid":1650210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再次謹記”不篤灰不割席不指責” 我地就可以贏","createTime":"2019-10-13T00:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T01:38:05.000Z","uid":18057,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"767f689512fb29cf7199b9113bfa015e36361067","tid":1650210,"uid":18057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:44:24.000Z","msg":"肯道歉認錯會改善 我地就比機會 <br />\n呢個係我地細細個已經知既道理<br />\n<br />\n一個三萬隻狗既紀律部隊 有哂系統 都經常錯都離撚哂譜<br />\n我地係最少有二百萬人既群眾 <br />\n偶爾有野做得唔太恰當 係咪就要咁樣呢 <br />\n希望唔好再講咩豬隊友 要唔要都罷<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隊友 多一個就好多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n政府六月到而家用不同手段要我地割 例如有大台 話前線破壞 暴力 目的好明顯係要不斷削弱我地戰力<br />\n如果今次咁樣就割 即係直接話比對家知呢個係弱點<br />\n我地係應該話比對家知我地真係核彈都唔割令佢地束手無策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad01fc95649ff3c1375ea438cc8d6900e604d71b","tid":1650210,"uid":18057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cb5aa8513fb3fef9d6102eeba602b156650ed6","tid":1650210,"uid":6991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油加油"},{"pid":"a24d2e597a2bda8eeba28b48c757ed1855b54bca","tid":1650210,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc85bbc6bedd415fae758b8871224f0e9c16ed3","tid":1650210,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:03:05.000Z","msg":"岩！！"},{"pid":"7d36ce63101e7f78ef1d84f3107a0f6c3f179991","tid":1650210,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化！<br />\n不完美 可改善"},{"pid":"bdffb7d2443146f313facbf0ca6c8ae3ae5d1d9b","tid":1650210,"ui